<h2 class="bac">Training:</h2>
<p class="bac">
The Technology Analyst Industrial Placement Program begins with a few days of orientation and induction to the company, and includes:
</p>
<ul class="bac">
	<li>Access to pre&ndash;work via an online e&ndash;learning portal covering foundation topics</li>
	<li>Relevant continuous training sessions over the Industrial Placement period </li>
	<li>Business critical assignments</li>
	<li>Exposure to senior leadership teams</li>
	<li>Networking and social events</li>
</ul>

